{"tid":2073872,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[ Forged in Fire : Beat the Judges 千錘百煉/鍛刀大賽 : 終於可以挑評判機 ]","createTime":"2020-06-21T15:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T11:50:26.000Z","uid":69994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"acffc076b420045610a2164093f05c73315ba5e8","tid":2073872,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:56:36.000Z","msg":"無印由 2015年 第1季 去到 第7季 第31集 暫時告一段落 S07 E31 ( 06-May-2020 ) .<br />\n<br />\n外傳 BEAT THE JUDGES 於 03-Jun-2020 開始 , 評判下海 ! 歷集冠軍回來挑機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> !<br />\n每集有 3 位前任冠軍回來參賽 , 曾兩輪撕殺後 , 剩下 1 位參賽者對決 1 位評判 ( 不包括 Doug Marcaida ) , 8 小時內完成作品 .<br />\n依然係 1 萬美元獎金 , 不過如果係評判贏 , 評判要捐曬慈善 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0G1JxpD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0G1JxpD.png&h=408a9e2f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SBWNeCZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSBWNeCZ.png&h=7672e8f2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>S01 E01 ( 03-Jun-2020 ) Short Sword Damascus</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n參賽者 : John Summerhill , Ethan Kempf , Kelly Vermeer Vella<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZE3xpX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZE3xpX.png&h=7b2f5de3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對決評判 Ben Abbott<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0D4fowH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0D4fowH.png&h=1fd97af6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>S01 E02 ( 10-Jun-2020 ) Medieval Times</ins></span><br />\n<blockquote></blockquote><br />\n參賽者 : Mark Knapp , Josh Navarrete , Steven Bryan<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FMhTUDG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFMhTUDG.png&h=72db91f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對決評判 David Baker<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1g8cqLq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1g8cqLq.png&h=f7befa7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>S01 E03 ( 17-Jun-2020 ) Duel Swords</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n參賽者 : Burt Foster , Jeff Wagenaar , John McNerney<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yhmacqu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhmacqu.png&h=eb915227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對決評判 J. Neilson<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g6VRGiU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg6VRGiU.png&h=045be650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBurt Foster 話當年 J. Neilson 考升級 Master Smith (MS) 時 , 他就是在席評審 !<br />\n之前 Burt Foster 回來參加 Champion of Champions 那一集時被 J. Neilson 挑中淘汰 , 就有點懷恨 , Burt Foster 這次就言明想挑戰 Ben Abbott , 因為那一集最後就是 Ben Abbott 贏了 , 當了第一個 Two-time Forged in Fire Champion !"},{"pid":"ab0217e74f96f0120f58fe1b6128b5bea90cb6a8","tid":2073872,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"BT :<br />\n<a href=\"https://eztv.io/search/forged-in-fire-beat-the-judges\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feztv.io%2Fsearch%2Fforged-in-fire-beat-the-judges&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=3d2dd38e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eztv.io/search/forged-in-fire-beat-the-judges</a><br />\n<br />\nYoutube :<br />\nE01 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iANO-h9zPDM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiANO-h9zPDM&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=661e036d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iANO-h9zPDM</a><br />\nE02 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K4GHSF2nkfk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DK4GHSF2nkfk&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=6165fe33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K4GHSF2nkfk</a><br />\nE03 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6G73H1y8Z3g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6G73H1y8Z3g&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=c5f232b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6G73H1y8Z3g</a><br />\nYoutube 應該很快被刪吧 , 而且第一集欠缺後半段 .<br />\n不過 Youtube 可以開人工字幕 (CC) , 揀翻譯中文都有 8 成準確 ( judges 翻譯成了法官... )"},{"pid":"f50ef9689ca221895f22b0273d5b61ad30c86fbc","tid":2073872,"uid":69994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T11:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dwwtQfb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdwwtQfb.gif&h=9bd2b4ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hJ3624.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hJ3624.jpg&h=38e62d09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"507792eea374bb0f21cbb4675f3823cb166ed1e8","tid":2073872,"uid":185184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T11:59:43.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇第一季嘅Ryu Lim呢<br />\n型撚到痴線"},{"pid":"b286d2ce83eed26f68707b75c6602631ff064b64","tid":2073872,"uid":297139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"我記得有一集係全部人都廢喎<br />\n冇記錯冠軍賽條友把長劍拎出黎斬隻豬一下就彎左<br />\n但對手果把唔知係斷左定未完成直接輸左<br />\n呢條友都有得出黎?"},{"pid":"83631f54901931d9c0996adbb2c8b37994391533","tid":2073872,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"有冇youtube果件長髮俄佬"},{"pid":"a1a37dec6fd5c7f0e1df6f26041a0bc19bf7f525","tid":2073872,"uid":69994,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b286d2ce83eed26f68707b75c6602631ff064b64","tid":2073872,"uid":297139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"我記得有一集係全部人都廢喎<br />\n冇記錯冠軍賽條友把長劍拎出黎斬隻豬一下就彎左<br />\n但對手果把唔知係斷左定未完成直接輸左<br />\n呢條友都有得出黎?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"唔知 , 無講係評判邀請 , 抑或開放給所有前冠軍自薦 .<br />\n我自己估就邀請 , 以節目製作角度睇 , 有得揀當然好D , fans 多既盡量分布唔同集數 .<br />\n<br />\n我粗略計過之前有150集左右 , 當有 150 個冠軍 , 而家每集 3 個冠軍返黎 , 如果一半人返黎 , 可以做到 20 集左右 .<br />\n<br />\n第 5 / 6 / 7 季 , 好多時一兩個業餘兩三年經驗後生仔 , 夾兩個全職廿年刀匠 , 一齊比初賽 , 可能因為指定古怪材料所以衰左 , 或者尺寸問題衰左 , 全職刀匠就輸得好樣衰 , 仲點做生意 . 二來有實力又有興趣出鏡既刀匠 , 頭幾季都出得七七八八 , 後期所謂全職 , 實力參差不齊 .<br />\n<br />\n而家呢輯 Beat the Judges , 返黎既全部前冠軍 , 淘汰都唔失禮 , 一個唔覺意贏埋評判 , 吸引力仲高過個獎金 ! 到時就唔係 &quot;我見過 Steve Jobs&quot; 而係 &quot;我贏過 Steve Jobs&quot; !"},{"pid":"5c1930728a513db2e2b32e7fc3613ea67706f233","tid":2073872,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"507792eea374bb0f21cbb4675f3823cb166ed1e8","tid":2073872,"uid":185184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T11:59:43.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇第一季嘅Ryu Lim呢<br />\n型撚到痴線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:36:52.000Z","msg":"製作組一定知邊d參賽者受歡迎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今個星期三 24-Jun-2020 ( S01 E04 ) 就呢 3 個 , 大家認唔認得 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxvqTGs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxvqTGs.png&h=1a5da89b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QqMp9eP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQqMp9eP.png&h=729f491e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sm9rC78.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsm9rC78.png&h=b1c92eaf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rvb9AUP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRvb9AUP.png&h=7f820cc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acfb60de55b0748bc2556643170b6d4cc1cbb4f6","tid":2073872,"uid":185184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c1930728a513db2e2b32e7fc3613ea67706f2